svg.title: Penang Island textured model CSS3 animation
svg.desc: Rotating textured pseudo-3D model of Penang Island, animated by CMG Lee using elevation data from http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Penang_Island_heightmap_ASTGTM2_N05E100_dem.png and bitmap from http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:LANDSAT_semenanjung_malaysia_-_2.jpg .
